<section class="about-section">
  <p>Welcome to my portfolio!</p>
  <h1>I'm a software engineer that loves creating innovative solutions.</h1>

  <div class="image-box">
    <img src="/images/about.PNG" alt="about-image" />
  </div>

  <h4>In this section, you'll learn more about my background and experience.</h4>
  <h5>  I'm dedicated to delivering high-quality software solutions.</h5>

</section>


<style>
    .about-section {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        margin-top: 200px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
    }
    
    .image-box {
        width: 360px;
        height: 510px;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 50px;
    }
    
    .image-box img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .about-section p {
        font-size: 12px;
    }

    .about-section h1 {
        font-family: Impact, Haettenschweiler, 'Arial Narrow Bold', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 100px;
        max-width: 1150px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 25px 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #4acfee, #53f8c9, #6070fd, #2a46ff, #4acfee);
        background-size: 200%;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        animation: animate-gradient 2.5s linear infinite;
        animate-gradient
    }


    @keyframes animate-gradient {
        to {
            background-position: 200%;
        }
    }

    

</style>
